name: Cherry Yu
bio:
I love travelling a lot! I'm welcome talk to people who have the same interest!

Here are over thirties countries I have been to over the last 6 yrs! I have just been to Italy which I love a lot! 
1. Cervinia for ski - Italy (Dec 2011)
2. Milan and small cities around like Verona, Lake Como and Bellagio - Italy (Dec 2011)
3. France (Aug 2011 for a mth) - Paris, Rennes, St Malo, Dinan, Fougeres, Mont St Michel, Deauville, Trouville, Cabourg, Houlgate, Villers sur Mer, Metz, Strasbourg, Colmar, Nancy
4. Belgium - Brussels, Bruges, Ghent, Antwerp (Aug 2011)
5. Luxembourg (Aug 2011)
6. Spain - Madrid and Barcelona
7. London
8. Rome, Venice - Italy
9. Holland
10. Greece - Athens, Mykonos, Santorini Island
